                            >Get a Quote</span
                        >
                    </a>
                    <a
                        href="/about"
                        class="group relative inline-flex items-center overflow-hidden rounded-full border-2 border-[#344CB7] px-8 py-3 text-[#344CB7] focus:outline-none focus:ring active:text-[#2d43a3]"
                    >
