                            >Learn More</span
                        >
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="relative">
                <div class="relative h-[600px] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
                    <img
                        src="/home/hero-ship.jpg"
                        alt="Alcanza Ship Services"
                        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                    />
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#344CB7]/50 to-transparent"
                    >
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Featured Services - Updated with card design -->
    <section class="py-20">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-black">Featured Services</h2>
            <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-[#344CB7] mx-auto mt-4"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            {
                services.map((service) => (
                    <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-xl">
                        <div class="relative h-64">
                            <img
                                src={service.image}
                                alt={service.title}
                                class="h-full w-full object-cover transition duration-500 group-hover:scale-105"
                            />
                            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#344CB7]/80 to-transparent" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="absolute bottom-0 p-8 text-white w-full">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">
                                {service.title}
                            </h3>
                            <a
                                href={service.link}
                                class="inline-flex items-center text-white hover:text-white/80"
                            >
                                Learn More
                                <svg
                                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                    class="h-5 w-5 ml-2"
                                    viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                                    fill="currentColor"
                                >
                                    <path
                                        fill-rule="evenodd"
                                        d="M12.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z"
                                        clip-rule="evenodd"
                                    />
                                </svg>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                ))
            }
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Who We Are - Updated with modern layout -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-gray-100">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
                <div class="space-y-8 p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
                    <div
                        class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#344CB7]/10 text-[#344CB7] rounded-full text-sm font-semibold"
                    >
                        About Us
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-black">Who we are?</h2>
                    <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-[#344CB7]"></div>
                    <p class="text-xl text-black leading-relaxed">
                        Sevenseas with its strong presence in ship chandling has
                        established itself as a trusted partner in the maritime
                        industry. With over two decades of experience, we've
                        built an extensive network of suppliers and logistics
                        partners across major ports. Our commitment to quality
                        service, competitive pricing, and timely delivery has
                        made us a preferred choice for vessel operators
                        worldwide. We specialize in providing comprehensive ship
                        supplies, technical stores, and provisions while
                        maintaining the highest standards of quality and
                        reliability.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="space-y-8">
                    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
                        <span
                            class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#344CB7]/10 text-[#344CB7] rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-4"
                        >
                            Our Journey
                        </span>
                        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-black mb-8">
                            What Makes Us Special
                        </h2>
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6">
                            {
                                features.map((feature) => (
                                    <div class="flex items-start space-x-4 p-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-300">
                                        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                                            <span class="text-4xl bg-[#344CB7]/10 w-14 h-14 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                                                {feature.icon}
                                            </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div>
                                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900">
                                                {feature.title}
                                            </h3>
                                            <p class="text-gray-600">
                                                {feature.description}
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                ))
                            }
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Supply Chain Services - Updated with modern cards -->
    <section class="py-20">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-black">Supply Chain Services</h2>
            <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-[#344CB7] mx-auto mt-4"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            {
                supplyChainServices.map((service, index) => (
                    <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300">
                        <div class="relative h-64">
                            <img
                                src={service.image}
                                alt={service.title}
                                class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105"
                            />
